---
import GuideLayout from "../../layouts/GuideLayout.astro";

const title = "After Builders Cleaning Checklist (Room by Room)";
const description = "Room-by-room checklist for cleaning a property after renovation or building work.";
---

<GuideLayout title={title} description={description} cluster="after-builders">

<p>After builders cleaning requires a systematic approach to remove construction dust from every surface.</p>

<h2>Kitchen</h2>
<p>Clean cabinets, appliances, surfaces and flooring to remove construction residue.</p>

<h2>Bathrooms</h2>
<p>Remove dust from tiles, fixtures and ventilation areas.</p>

<h2>Living Areas</h2>
<p>Vacuum floors, wipe surfaces and clean windows to remove plaster dust.</p>

</GuideLayout>
